to run on railway =============

run: railway init 

ensure procfile ===========================

web: npm run dev

edit nixpacks.toml ===================

[phases.setup]
nixPkgs = ["nodejs_18"]

[phases.install]
cmds = ["npm install"]

[phases.build]
cmds = []

then upload to railway ==================

run: railway up

to STOP the railway app ===========

run: railway down



Railway will auto detect updates to github. and redeploy




